<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="th">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, maximum-scale=1, user-scalable=no">
    <meta name="description" content="">
    <meta name="keywords" content="">
    <title>BluePay</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
<div id="wrap">
    <div id="main-content">
        <div id="_logo">
            <div class="container">
                {% if prePage is not empty %}
                    <div style="color:#48A7FF;height: 20px;width: 150px;position: absolute;z-index: 2;top: 15px;">
                        <a href="{{ prePage }}"><img src="/img/Back.png" style="padding:0px 10px;margin:0px;width: 39px;height: 24px;float: left;"><!--pilih tarif yang lain--></a>
                    </div>
                {% endif %}
                <div class="col-md-12">
                    <img src="/img/bluePay_logo.png" class="center-block img-responsive">
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div id="_sub-content" style="box-shadow: 0px 0px 0px #FFFFFF; border-bottom: 2px dashed #D1EDFF; padding-bottom:10px;">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="contentatmTop">
                    <p class="input-lg myclass" style="font-size:16px;">Bayar di Mini Market</p>
                    <span class="input-lg myclass" style="font-size:11px;">Catatan : Silahkan Lakukan Pembayaran di Alfa Group (Alfamart, Alfamidi, LAWSON, DAN+DAN)</span>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-12">
                    <form id="offlineFormID" method="get" action="">
                        <div class="input-lg myclass">Harga Barang <span>Rp.{{ price|number_format }}</span></div>
                        <div class="input-lg myclass">Blaya Transaksi <span id="myspanriceID">{{ fee }}</span></div>
                        <div class="input-lg myclass">Jumlah Tagihan <span id="myspantotallID">Rp.{{ price }}</span></div>
                    </form>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div id="_sub-content" style="box-shadow: 0px 0px 0px #FFFFFF; padding: 0px;">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="col-md-12">
                    <form id="offlineFormID" method="get" action="" style="margin-top:-10px;padding-bottom:15px;">
                        <div class="input-lg myclass" >Kode Transaksi:<hr  style="margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;"/>
                            <span style="width:100%; text-align:right; font-family: 'HelveticaNeue-Medium';font-size: 16px;color: deepskyblue;letter-spacing: -1px;line-height: 23px;">
                                {{ paymentcode }}
                            </span>
                        </div>
                    </form>
                </div>
            </div>
            {% if redirect_url is not empty  %}
                <a href="{{ redirect_url|trim }}"><div class="confirmClass">OK</div></a>
            {% endif %}
        </div>
        <div class="contentfooot">
            <p>1.Pergi ke Alfa Group</p>
            <p>2. Katakan Kepada Kasir Ingin Melakukan Pembayaran Transaksi Online “BLUEPAY”, Sebutkan Jumlah Tagihan ({{ price+fee }}) dan Kode Transaksi ({{ paymentcode }})</p>
            <P>3. Kasir Akan Melakukan Konfirmasi dan Menyebutkan Nominal Yang Harus Dibayar</P>
            <P>4. Lakukan Pembayaran ke Kasir dan Dapatkan Struk Bukti Pembayaran, Setelah 1-3 Menit Barang Akan Otomatis Terkirim di Dalam Aplikasi</P>
        </div>


    </div>
</div>
<div id="footer">
    <div class="sub-footer">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-12">
                    <p class="text-center">&copy; <a href="#" title="BlueMobile">Blue Mobile Tech</a> Co.,Ltd. All rights reserved.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<!-- jQuery (necessary for Bootstrap's JavaScript plugins) -->
<script src="/js/jquery.min.js"></script>
<!-- Include all compiled plugins (below), or include individual files as needed -->
<script src="/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
<script src="/js/bluepay.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
    var productId = "{{ productId }}";
    if (!showLogo(productId)) {
        $("#_logo").css("display","none");
    };
</script>
</body>
</html>